{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_04_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 仲間から刺激を受けて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2……ここで、ターン！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2… Here‚ turn!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei001-01.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、こんな感じでオッケーかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mhm‚ mhm‚ like this‚ OK.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、次は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ next is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2700.000000000001,
          "startTime": 16.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333333999985,
          "startTime": 16.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ good job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！\n他のみんなは帰ったよー？　どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san!\nEveryone else leaved~ What's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣に用があったんだよ\n最近、練習を凄く頑張ってるみたいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had something to discuss with you‚ Mei.\nIt seems like you've been working really hard in practice lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうなんだー\nちょっと気合いを入れようと思って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that's right!\nI wanted to put more effort into it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなも凄いと言ってたんだが……\nあまりにも熱心だから、ちょっと心配もしてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other members of Moon Tempest also mentioned how amazing you are…\nI was a little worried because you were so dedicated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは。確かに最近、みんなによく心配されてたなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. Yeah‚ recently everyone has been expressing their concern for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "今日なんて、レッスンの後\n沙季ちゃんに大の字に寝かされてさー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like today‚ after the lesson‚\nSaki-chan made me lie down in a star shape…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "四人がかりでマッサージされちゃった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then all four of them massaged me together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なかなか凄い光景だな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quite a scene…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "気持ち良かったよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It felt really good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}さんに相談したってことは\nみんなよっぽど心配してたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if they told {user}-san about me‚\nit means everyone was really worried about me‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "後で謝っておかないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll apologize to them later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なんでそんなに頑張ってるのか……\n良かったら聞かせてくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you working so hard…\nIf it's okay‚ could you tell me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも、あと十分だけ練習していい？\n心配なら見てていいから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but can I practice for another ten minutes?\nIf you're worried‚ you can watch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、待ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I'll wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 93.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 93.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "この間、すずにゃんが麻奈ちゃんの曲を\nカバーしたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day‚\nSuzu-nyan covered Mana-chan's song‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……練習でもめきめき成長してたけど\n本番はさらに輝いていたな。俺も驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… She has been improving a lot during practice‚\nbut she was even more radiant during the actual performance. I was surprised too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "歌ももちろん凄かったんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her singing was amazing‚ of course‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 108.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "それ以上に、すずにゃんは本当に\n麻奈ちゃんのことが好きなんだなーって思ってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but more than that‚ Suzu-nyan\nreally seems to like Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 118.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら芽衣も、麻奈ちゃんと過ごした時間とか\nもう会えなくなった時のこととか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That made me remember… things like the time I spent with Mana-chan and\nwhen we couldn't meet anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんみたいなアイドルになりたいって\n言ってたこと……改めて思い出したんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said that I wanted to become an idol like Mana-chan…\nIt all came rushing back to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 136.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、なんだか体がムズムズして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ I felt this tingling sensation in my body‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 140.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "今出来ることをやらなきゃ！\n麻奈ちゃんみたいになるぞー！　って思ったんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "like I have to do what I can now!\nI thought‚ \"I want to become like Mana-chan!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.71,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな、すずのライブに刺激された訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ you were inspired by Suzu's live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 151.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_01-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　それで、どうしたら麻奈ちゃん\nみたいになれるかなーって考えたんだけど",
